    "description": "At Ganashri Oil Merchants, we bring you pure and traditionally wood-pressed edible oils, crafted using the ancient Lakdi Gani method to ensure maximum nutrient retention. Our oils are extracted at room temperature, preserving the natural antioxidants, rich aroma, and authentic flavor that modern processing loses. We take pride in producing high-quality Groundnut, Safflower, Coconut, Sunflower, Sesame, Flaxseed, Mustard, and Castor Oils, alongside nutrient-rich Groundnut Cake for cattle feed. Every drop of Ganashri oil is 100% chemical-free, unrefined, and meticulously filtered to guarantee purity, freshness, and trust. Choose Ganashri for a chemical-free kitchen and a legacy of health that your family deserves.",
    
